Mahadev is always with you. You don’t have to be the strongest you just need to remember the source.🙏🔱✨

latestPosts.caption:
They say the soul never forgets where it first felt free. Mine remembered and it took me to Kashi.🔱
Where the Ganga doesn’t just cleanse the body,
but strips the ego bare. Where every alley is a prayer,
and every sunrise feels like forgiveness.
You don’t visit Kashi. You surrender to it.
And somewhere in the chaos,
you hear your soul whisper,
“This!! this is where I leave the noise behind.”🔱🤍 #varanasi #kashi #banaras 
.

Hanuman ji, the embodiment of courage and devotion, carried the Sanjeevani with unwavering strength! A reminder that divine protection is beyond logic, beyond limits.
Tomorrow is Shani Jayanti, and there’s no better time to remember this truth:  Even Shani Dev bows before Hanuman ji Because Hanuman’s name, once spoken with true faith, can calm even the fiercest planets 🪐 
and turn obstacles into blessings.

Jai Bajrang Bali 🙏
